## üéØ UX Principles

### Performance-First UX
- **Sub-200ms interactions** for all UI elements
- **Skeleton loading states** with rust accents
- **Progressive image loading** with blur-to-sharp transitions
- **Optimistic UI updates** for immediate feedback
- **Smooth 60fps animations** throughout

### Accessibility Standards
- **WCAG 2.1 AA compliance** minimum
- **High contrast ratios** (especially with rust on black)
- **Keyboard navigation** for all interactive elements
- **Screen reader optimization** with proper ARIA labels
- **Reduced motion support** for accessibility preferences

