## üîß Implementation Guidelines

### CSS-in-JS vs Tailwind
- **Use Tailwind CSS** for utility-first styling in [apps/web](mdc:apps/web)
- **CSS modules** for component-specific styles in [apps/desktop](mdc:apps/desktop)
- **CSS custom properties** for theme consistency across both apps
- **Rust color utilities** available as Tailwind classes

### Animation Standards
```css
/* Smooth, performant animations */
.fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.2s ease-out; }
.slide-up { animation: slideUp 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); }
.rust-glow { 
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(205, 127, 50, 0.3);
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}
```

### Retina & High-DPI Support
- **2x/3x image assets** for all icons and graphics
- **SVG icons** preferred over raster images
- **High-resolution screenshots** for game previews
- **Crisp text rendering** with proper font smoothing

